message.content:
I need to identify the financing costs incurred by the enterprise to raise funds needed for production and operation from the income statement.

In financial reporting, these costs are typically captured under "Financial Expenses" which represent the cost of borrowing money and other financing-related costs.

Looking at the income statement provided, I can see that there is a line item labeled "Financial Expenses" with a value of 50283.07 dated 2024-02-05.

This is the value I need to extract as it represents the financing costs incurred by the enterprise.

```json
{"solution": {'value': '50283.07'}}
```
